The Best Of Head-Cracker's Maps!

To instal extract to "...\Steam\steamapps\account-name\counter-strike source\cstrike"

This map pack include:

aim_p2w - Simple aim map.
awp_india_v2 - AWP + Knifes.
fy_cubeassault_v2 - A little fight yard map, which, as name says, is a little cube.
fy_triplearena_v2 - One map, three very different arenas. You pick which one you wanna fight.
fy_train - A simple fight yard map with 4 trains moving around the map. Beware!
he_arena - Small grenade arena.
ka_airdrop2 - Knife arena map.
ka_fallingtrash - Knife arena map with some suprises! Look up!
ka_glassfloor - Knifes + Nades + Glass floor = FUN FUN FUN.
scoutzknivez_hc - My version of scoutzknivez. 

Hope you like it! :)

Any QQ: headcracker@gmail.com or http://www.fpsbanana.com/members/24315

Thanks.

Head-Cracker
